item.title: Woman trainer found dead at PT Usha’s athletics school in ‘suspected suicide’
item.description: Woman trainer found dead at PT Usha’s athletics school in ‘suspected suicide’ A 27-year-old woman trainer was found dead at the hostel of the Usha School of Athletics in Kozhikode Friday in a “suspected suicide”, said the police.
